::Zardus/DeathStorm/DevilDuer::

Zardus looks at Blue Reeker, his eyes resting briefly on her sleek shape. 
"Excelent job."

He looks around at the rest of the alliance members there. "Return back to 
base." He orders and walks transforms to beast mode, flying off toward the 
alliance base.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DeathStorm picks up DevilDuer, leaving Crow Lord's corpse behind, and flies 
off after Zardus.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Bloodystrike, Reptilica, and Perndabot walk off toward the alliance base.
